column5: 8 Minute to Down Town, 6th Street / Congress Mini fridge, microwave, coffee pot in Room. Room for 1 or 2 Adults. A basket of snacks, tea/coffee provided. Large window with nature view of deer and bunnies. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood next to one of Austin's popular greenbelt / nature trails.  1 mile to Restaurants,Bars and Shops.
column8: Quiet Area - 8 min to D.T. Q-Bed, fridge/micro
